title: Anvil - Absolutely No Alternative (Japanese Version) [FLAC]
description:
This is the rare Japanese pressing of Anvil's 1997 album "Absolutely No Alternative", complete with two extra tracks not found anywhere else.

For maximum enjoyment, this album has been ripped in EAC and encoded in FLAC and for proof of authenticity, I scanned some of the album's artwork.

Fans of Anvil and classic Heavy Metal will definitely enjoy this rare release in lossless form
